{"tid":1914941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中蟈人工吞噬吞噬取代俄國軍事]愛沙尼亞的武漢肺炎確診急增至10宗","createTime":"2020-03-08T00:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T05:30:54.000Z","uid":100986,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f52124b0511b3c222eaf1ab93436a2f6a5b00ab","tid":1914941,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T00:17:39.000Z","msg":"[中蟈人工病毒吞噬已經正式取代了俄羅斯軍事力量，中蟈成為愛沙尼亞、波蘭、立陶宛和拉脫維亞的頭號對手]<br />\n愛沙尼亞的武漢肺炎確診個案急增至10宗<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.err.ee/photo/crop/2020/02/27/753489hf229t62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.err.ee%2Fphoto%2Fcrop%2F2020%2F02%2F27%2F753489hf229t62.jpg&h=b05eee33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe total number of cases of COVID-19 coronavirus detected in Estonia has risen to ten. Of the latest cases, the two announced earlier this morning were on the same flight from Bergamo, Italy along with two cases identified earlier in the week. Five more confirmed cases have been reported since then.<br />\n<br />\nThe Health Board has itemized all those Estonians on the Bergamo-Riga flight on February 29, and analyzed a total of 10 samples, including the new positive cases, on Thursday.<br />\n<br />\nCoronavirus figure in Estonia rises to ten<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.err.ee/1060592/coronavirus-figure-in-estonia-rises-to-ten\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.err.ee%2F1060592%2Fcoronavirus-figure-in-estonia-rises-to-ten&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=b03599f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.err.ee/1060592/coronavirus-figure-in-estonia-rises-to-ten</a>"},{"pid":"606e8150164e42f500138e38e5f34feef97b5f96","tid":1914941,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T00:22:34.000Z","msg":"波蘭頂住啊⋯⋯"},{"pid":"f090216df8d5209fb9b5eba5ec7c9b5fc3160580","tid":1914941,"uid":100986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"606e8150164e42f500138e38e5f34feef97b5f96","tid":1914941,"uid":346806,"like":1